<plot>A dramedy in ten minutes. On an everyday trip to the grocery store, Charlie is standoffish with Blanche, a perfect stranger who insists he looks exactly like her deceased son. Charlie ultimately empathizes with Blanche and manages to share a kernel of his own broken past, only to realize in retrospect that Blanche isn't at all what she seemed.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?494272</url></doc>
